version_description: This is all of the aspects of the song in one piece, so that nobody has to switch between 2 for the entire song.
For acoustic guitar acompaniment / introducing piano movements with the vocals and turnarounds / intermediate with sus4 and split chords.
I have included B7/D# and G/D to chorus which as i hear it is spot on,i have also added chords to the verses which i believe are more accurate.
The first few versions had too many seventh chords and were incomplete.
Electric guitar with Fuzz effect,gain turned down a little, palm mute A chords to help give a basic rhythm through song.
